{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.15.1515;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\cf1\b\f0\fs20 When a data source is set to Access=\cf2 Read\cf1 , the values cannot be updated even if they are allowed to be modified.\par
\par
In this example, the variables can be modified, but the values are not saved, and an error message is generated. Usually in such a situation, modify would not be allowed. But read-only ensures that no modify will happen in any case, and also ensures that there will be less record locking and data access will be faster.\par
}
